///hangman game pseudocode

create an array of words
get a random word from an array
create a for loop



///how to play hangman

///the computer has a hidden word that is chosen randomly
///computer will display blank spaces based on number of characters in the word
///user is trying to guess the word by entering random letters

///the computer will compare the users character guesses to the individual characters in the randomly chosen word

///if user guesses a character which is included in the randomly chosen word, the computer will display the character as it appears in the word in the corresponding blank of that character

///if user guesses a correct character, piece of hangman will appear


///if user completes correct guesses and completes word, then user wins

///if user wins, hangman image completes 

///


